# Test Plan

# Test Plan: CrossClip

1. Objective
The objective of this testing is to verify that CrossClip functions correctly across authentication, clipboard management, synchronization, and UI interactions.

1. Scope

Features to be tested:

- Authentication
- Clipboard item creation
- Clipboard deletion
- Clipboard pinning
- Clipboard filtering
- Clipboard history limit
- Realtime synchronization
- UI responsiveness

1. Testing Type
- Manual testing
- Functional testing
- UI testing
- Edge case testing
- Exploratory testing

1. Test Environment

Application URL: ([https://cross-clip.vercel.app/](https://cross-clip.vercel.app/))

Browsers:

- Chrome
- Brave
- Microsoft Edge
- Safari

Devices:

- Desktop
- Mobile

1. Risks
- Network latency affecting sync
- Large file uploads
- Mobile responsiveness issues
